reviewText: This is the standard by which all other videos in this genre should be measured.

The Amazon photo of this DVD's box showed me I probably wanted to buy this DVD, for it has Michelle Maylene, Tiffany Brooks and Jennifer Lee (a.k.a. Christine Nguyen). It wasn't disappointing, for it has some of Michelle's and Tiffany's sexiest scenes yet, and Jennifer was good in it too. I'm indeed glad I was able to find and buy it. I saw previews of it on some Peach DVDs I bought some time ago, so I knew I wanted this one when I found it on Amazon. There are 2 or 3 other girls on it, but the ones on the box are my favorites by far.
